# Run all tests
pytest tests/ -v

# Run specific test categories
pytest tests/algorithms/ -v
pytest tests/data_structures/ -v
pytest tests/performance/ -v

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=algorithms --cov=data_structures tests/

# Run property-based tests
pytest tests/property_based/ -v

Performance Benchmarks
Run comprehensive benchmarks:

python benchmarks/run_all_benchmarks.py



Example output:

==========================================
Algorithm Benchmark Results
==========================================
Sorting Algorithms:
- QuickSort: 1000 elements - 0.45ms
- MergeSort: 1000 elements - 0.52ms
- TimSort: 1000 elements - 0.38ms

Graph Algorithms:
- Dijkstra (Eager): 1000 vertices - 12.3ms
- Dijkstra (Lazy): 1000 vertices - 15.7ms
- A* Search: 1000 vertices - 18.2ms


Documentation
Generate documentation:


cd docs
make html
# Open docs/_build/html/index.html


Or view online: Documentation

Project Structure


algovault/
├── algorithms/              # Algorithm implementations
│   ├── sorting/           # Sorting algorithms
│   ├── searching/         # Search algorithms
│   ├── graph/            # Graph algorithms
│   ├── dynamic/          # Dynamic programming
│   ├── string/           # String algorithms
│   └── math/             # Mathematical algorithms
├── data_structures/       # Data structure implementations
├── visualizations/        # Interactive visualizations
├── benchmarks/           # Performance benchmarks
├── tests/               # Comprehensive test suite
├── notebooks/           # Jupyter notebooks
├── playground/          # Interactive playground
└── docs/               # Documentation
